[It would be advantageous for everyone involved for the nature of the tests
giving false positive results to be disclosed. Nothing will be gained by
secrecy. Until the situation is clarified, there will be uncertainty about
the accuracy of the diagnosis of the patient in Bladen county. -Mod.CP
